{
  "stem": "3103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because if they came to the border, they showed the documents, the truck driver, that you know, I think by the end of inside, they put some merchandise.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they didn't look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really don't remember deeper in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they brought us to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, in Germany, started a different life again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My parents were in Landsberg in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went my way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wanted to go to medical school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I went to Munich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I did bring my diplomas from Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a Jewish organization who were all-- even my husband was involved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They-- the guys were older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We took an entrance exam to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They quizzed me everything, and I passed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POLISH] in Polish, [POLISH]-- the students, basically old, elderly one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not elderly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, five, seven years older, that they were already at the university.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I passed my exam with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I needed Latin also, see which they didn't teach in Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those days, if you did write the prescription, you wrote yourself in Latin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went to a cloister and rang the doorbell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a father came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told him my story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, I need some tutoring for the entrance exam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he spent with me now almost every day for six months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got a little, as much as I needed it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at the time, I really wanted to become a pharmacist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in Munich, everything was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So there was an opening on dentistry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's what I accepted, and I became a dentist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, most of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this year, after 50 years, we have a reunion with all of them who survived now living in Israel, October the 24th.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
